137
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] kroz odrastanje ili si ustekao, razvio kroz sport?

138
00:13:39,500 --> 00:13:46,259
[SPEAKER_01] Ti kada dođeš, jedan dan sam jednom bivšem partneru,

139
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:48,299
